  return [200, JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(data.users)).reverse()];
}); // GET: Fetch Single User Details

mock.onGet(/\/api\/user-management\/users\/\d+/).reply(function (request) {
  var userId = request.url.substring(request.url.lastIndexOf("/") + 1);
  var user = data.users.find(function (user) {
    return user.id == userId;
  });
  return user ? [200, JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(user))] : [404];

mock.onDelete(/\/api\/user-management\/users\/\d+/).reply(function (request) {
  var userId = request.url.substring(request.url.lastIndexOf("/") + 1);
  var itemIndex = data.users.findIndex(function (p) {
    return p.id == userId;
  });
  data.users.splice(itemIndex, 1);
  return [200];
});
